  "description": "<i>Slap Happy Rhythm Busters</i> is a 1-on-1 fighting game featuring a trendy Shibuya style and cel-shaded graphics reminiscent of <a href=\"https://www.mobygames.com/game/jet-grind-radio\">Jet Set Radio</a>. Despite the 3D graphics, it is strictly a 2D fighter. Certain specially moves, dubbed &quot;Beat&quot; moves, introduce a slight rhythm element: the player must hit certain buttons in time with the music to land attacks, and better timing will lead to more damage dealt.<br><br>Included are a single-player Arcade mode, a Versus mode, a training mode, and a special practice mode for the Beat attacks. There are 11 characters initially available, plus a further 10 unlockable through the Arcade mode.",
